Class PropertiesObjectSerializer

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.serialization.properties.PropertiesObjectSerializer
All Implemented Interfaces:
TryCatchTrait, TryTrait, Broadcaster, Listener, MessageTransceiver, Repeater, RepeaterMixin, Transceiver, Receiver, Transmitter, Nameable, NamedObject, Mixin, ObjectReader, ObjectSerializer, ObjectWriter
public class PropertiesObjectSerializer extends Object implements ObjectSerializer
Reads a SerializableObject from a .properties file. Writing is not supported at this time.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
